properties.name: Up and Over
properties.description: Up and over from the MQ Courtyard to the Spittleberg area. Once over there, explore the streets between Siebenstergasse and Burgasse. Kirchberggasse, Gutenberggasse, Spittelberggasse, und so wieder.

properties.name: Raimundhof passage
properties.description: Starts at Mariahilferstrasse 75. Down stairs past small shops, restaurants, and bars

properties.name: MQ to Naschmarkt
properties.description: There are many ways to get from MQ to the Naschmarkt. This route starts down one of the pretty Vienna stairways, past the Top Kino, Phil, Cafe Sperl, and Puff. All of the small streets between the MQ and Naschmarkt are interesting for their shops, signs, stickers, and graffiti
